---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | 5.Y"
  description="5.Y Terms & Conditions - Please read these terms carefully before using our website and services."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.five-whys.com/terms"
  activeNav=""
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section style="padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: var(--color-bg-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 1.125rem;">Please read these terms carefully before using our website and services.</p>
    </section>

    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;">
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Welcome to the official website of 5Y Holdings Pte. Ltd. (5.Y). By accessing or using this site, you agree to the terms outlined below.</p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Basics</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The content provided on this website is intended for general informational purposes and may be modified at any time without prior notice. While we aim to ensure the accuracy of our content, we cannot guarantee that the site will always be error-free or uninterrupted. These Terms &amp; Conditions (T&amp;Cs) only apply to this website. 5.Y Products and Services are governed with separate T&amp;Cs.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Intellectual Property</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Some of the materials, including text, images, and branding, are the exclusive property of 5.Y. You may not copy, reproduce, modify, or distribute any content without prior written consent from 5.Y.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Cookies and Analytics</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">This website uses cookies and tracking technologies to improve functionality and analyze visitor behavior. By using this site, you consent to the use of cookies. For more details, please review our <a href="/privacy" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: underline;">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Third-Party Links</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">This website may include links to external websites for your convenience. 5.Y is not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of these third-party websites.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">5.Y is not liable for any damages arising from the use of this website, including errors, omissions, or reliance on third-party links.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Governing Law</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">These terms are governed by the laws of Singapore, the jurisdiction in which 5.Y operates.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Policy Updates</h3>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We may update these Terms &amp; Conditions periodically. Continued use of this website implies acceptance of the latest terms.</p>

      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">For any inquiries or concerns regarding these Terms &amp; Conditions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@five-whys.com" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: underline;">info@five-whys.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
